	<section id="eligibile">
		<div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
			<h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-8">Sectoare eligibile</h3>
			<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 text-center mb-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				Programul sprijină investițiile în șase ramuri industriale strategice, esențiale pentru modernizarea economiei Republicii Moldova:
			</p>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-gov-blue hover:shadow-lg transition-all cursor-pointer group">
					<div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full overflow-hidden mx-auto mb-4 border-4 border-white shadow-md">
						<img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/electronic/100/100" alt="Иконка: Электронная промышленность" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
					</div>
					<h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Industria electronică</h4>
					<p class="text-gray-600">Componente electronice, echipamente IT, sisteme automatizate</p>
				</div>

				<div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-gov-blue hover:shadow-lg transition-all cursor-pointer group">
